        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title></title>
</head>
<body style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="main" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 850px; min-height: 100vh; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
        <div class="main-content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 24px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; flex: 1 1 0%; display: flex; min-height: 100vh; flex-direction: column;">
            <div class="post-detail" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; flex: 1 1 0%;">
                <article class="post" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 24px 32px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">
                    <div class="post-content-wrapper" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex;">
                        <div class="post-content" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 738px; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: "Droid Serif", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Droid Sans Fallback", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;'>
                            <h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.42em; text-align: justify;">
                                <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                    <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">关于TIBUTI</font>
                                </font>
                            </h2>
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;"><code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Tibuti.cn，全国首个敢面向市场公开量化结果的站点。</strong></code></p><code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">Tibuti（&ldquo;t不t&rdquo;）主要以量化分析方法来测算股票未来的<code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>最高价格</code>，主张有预见、主见的做T增加盈利或提前规避大幅回撤。Tibuti策略实质就是围绕<code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>振幅</code>进行的深度量化研究：</p>
                                <h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.17em; text-align: justify;">振幅</h3>
                                <pre style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; text-align: justify;'><code class="language-python hljs" style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 1em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 0.96em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(249, 247, 243); border-radius: 5px; line-height: 1.5;'>振幅 = （ 最高价 - 最低价 ） &divide;  前一日收盘价
</code></pre>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
                                <h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.17em; text-align: justify;">最高价格</h3>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">最高价格探索的是股票振幅日内可<code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>T</code>空间，且对收盘结果持放任态度。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">最高价格是以一个精准到0.000001元的确定值展示而不是碰运气的弹性区间，真假两半掰，花一两个交易日的时间便可做出判断。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">1.Tibuti最高价格的测算实行的是确定值，对最低价格则实行参考值（尚不成熟暂不公开）。一旦触碰最高价格，实现第一步高卖，低买则需要自己去按照期望值实施，比如最高点卖出后下跌3%、4%再买入。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">Tibuti实行确定值的意义：一、便于直观甄别量化策略准不准；二、便于股民自己设置滑点。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">2.对收盘结果持放任态度是指不以收盘价来衡量策略的准确性，交易期内任意时间点达到Tibuti测算的最高价格就视策略有效。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
                                <h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.42em; text-align: justify;">&ldquo;T不T&rdquo;的 T</h2>
                                <h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.17em; text-align: justify;">关于红肥绿瘦</h3>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;"><code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Slogan:</strong> T否T否，应是红肥绿瘦。</code></p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">1.红肥：股票高卖低买（能挣多挣）</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">2.绿瘦：回落提前预判（少亏为盈）</p>
                                <h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.17em; text-align: justify;">做T与仓位</h3>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">1.本策略原则上研究的是在不改变仓位情况下做T高卖低买实现利润最大化且收盘时<code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>仓位不变</code>。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">做T包含两层意思：<br style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">1.1&nbsp;T一次：高位卖出，低位买回仓位</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">1.2T两次：低位买进，次高位卖出，再买进在第2高位卖出</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">相对于其他人分享了个寂寞不同，Tibuti弱化讲量化的逻辑和计算，直接分享T+1量化分析结果。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">目前可实现的策略有T+1（日）、T+5（周），T+5是T+1的同规则延伸，只分享T+1是因为日内交易更能体现策略的灵敏性，T+5相对保守适用于大仓位。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">2.既然可以通过绿瘦做到&ldquo;大幅回落提前预判&rdquo;，那能不能高卖后进行预判不恢复仓位好规避下一个交易日下跌？</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">技术手段已经可以实现。假定收盘前1-3分钟的股票价格只在1%范围内波动了，继而在策略里计算下一个交易日的策略值以判断是否恢复仓位。但是此方式受限于计算机计算能力还只适用于单只股票，如确有需要可以考虑增加计算机数量来分批计算。</p>
                                <h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.17em; text-align: justify;">严肃的现实问题</h3>
                                <h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1em; text-align: justify;">因小失大</h4>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">不论是基于何种交易思路做T都有T了后又大涨的情形，这在量化分析的逻辑里也无法完全避免，间接的避免方式如采取小仓位T，成功了皆大欢喜，失败了就失败了投资本就如此。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">出现测算最高价低于实际最高价格的原因是Tibuti的策略是按照同一规则无差别去计算A股全部股票，考虑到了共同性特征而没能兼顾个性特征，这就需要采纳策略的股民因势而为，自主考虑<code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>滑点</code>。</p>
                                <pre style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; text-align: justify;'><code class="language-python hljs" style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 1em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 0.96em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(249, 247, 243); border-radius: 5px; line-height: 1.5;'>滑点 ：
<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">1.</span> 结合个股认为Tibuti的测算价过低，那就执行：最高价&times;<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">1.01</span>
<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">2.</span> 结合个股认为Tibuti的测算价过高，那就执行：最高价&times;<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">0.99</span>
<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">3.</span> 或者直接在测算价上加价或减价
</code></pre>
                                <h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1em; text-align: justify;">鼓吹做T</h4>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">做T势必增加交易成本，但是只考虑成本而忽略振幅范围内的高收益，难免颠倒了投资是追求更高收益的本质特征。我不鼓吹做T，我主张&ldquo;有预见、有主见的T&rdquo;，T一下最低能够实现2%的收益率就应认可为成功的T。<br style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
                                <h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.42em; text-align: justify;">评价标准</h2>
                                <h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.17em; text-align: justify;">准确率标准机制</h3>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">Tibuti策略评价标准，采用的是取<code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>任意</code><code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>93个交易日</code><code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>无差别计算</code>A股所有股票的日最高价格与实际最高价格偏差<code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>&le;1.5%</code>的准确率。</p>
                                <pre style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; text-align: justify;'><code class="language-python hljs" style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 1em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 0.96em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(249, 247, 243); border-radius: 5px; line-height: 1.5;'>关键词解读： 
<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">1.</span>任意：既考虑随机<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">93</span>个交易日的偏差也考虑连续<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">93</span>个交易日的偏差 
<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">2.</span>交易日<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">93</span>个：在策略设计之初是为了量化分析月（<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">31</span>个交易日）整体趋势但是月波动太大稳定性不高 后来进化到测算日最高价格时延用了<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">31</span>个交易日的思路并且认为<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">3</span>个周期的计算更稳定所以是<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">93</span>个交易日。 
<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">3.</span>无差别计算：所有计算过程都按照同一方式和逻辑进行，不区别对待或为某类型股票单独设立评价标准 
<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">4.</span>偏差&le;<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">1.5</span>%：如果偏差大于<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">1.5</span>%还要追求做T3%的收益那振幅至少得保证<span class="hljs-number" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">4.5</span>%，那参考价值就太低了 
</code></pre>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;<br style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>55.77%，是Tibuti策略目前相对稳定的准确率。</code></strong></p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">1.全部样本准确率：全部样本T+1最高价格误差率&le;1.5%的准确率为<code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>64.59%</code><br style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">2.清洗样本准确率：产生64.59%准确率的数据里包含了几百只主板振幅在1.5%以内的股票和明显被高估（涨幅超过了10%）的股票，清洗掉这部分数据后的平均准确率在55.77%。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
                                <h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.17em; text-align: justify;">浮动计算机制</h3>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">拥有了稳定有效的量化分析策略能不能收割股市了？当然不能，其局限性体现在三个方面：</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">1.量化分析是多对多的关系，一篮子策略。分析和交易都得多股票组合，有的涨有的跌，最后收益率在稳定性范围内这个策略才算有效。分析一堆票，最后选一只票，那不是量化的实质是赌，把把能赌对收割股市顶多算收割全球的一小步。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">2.量化策略也是因势而变，因子选择、因子参数、因子评价都是不断在变化的，只要准确率低于平均准确率就得改变主要参数。Tibuti策略会很好的利用浮动机制保证市场变则策略变。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">3.量化策略到底有没有用，除了量化策略本身之外还有一个重要因素--资金优势。即使策略前期失败，只要有足够资金补仓错误的策略也可以被反转。这一点可以说是国内众多假大空量化分析成绩展示的惯用套路，换句话说只要资金足够充足什么策略不那么关键，不soha就行。<br style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
                                <h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.42em; text-align: justify;">&ldquo;T不T&rdquo;的 不</h2>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">Tibuti.cn是<code style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0.125em; padding: 0.2em 0.333333em; font-family: "Source Code Pro", Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 1em; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 245, 245); color: rgb(197, 48, 48);'>一个人</code>的独立量化分析展示站点，环境和能力受限制于方方面面。在乐于分享的同时仍需强调几个我认为很关键的问题：</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">1.分享：不收费、不推票、不建群、不开课，对服务的及时性、出错发生不作保证。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">2.收入：只接受非私下交流前的打赏与捐赠，我比较倾向于这种一个陌生人对另一个陌生人表达认可的方式。另外为了鼓励自主打赏和捐赠，支付额排名靠前者可免费享受无固定期限的咨询（第3条除外），支付额可以是一次也可以是多次累计，排名靠前的标准取决于我那一刻的想法。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">打赏和捐赠支持100元以上金额7天无理由退款</strong></p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">3.拒绝：拒绝接受任何人、任何方式与我讨论量化分析结果本身之外的任何。</p>
                                <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.12em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.62; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; hyphens: auto; text-align: justify;">4.豁免：采取何种运营方式和收入方式只要在法律允许范围内尤其是不采取欺骗、诈骗情形的完全由我那一刻的想法决定。<br style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
